"""
Image Rater - IrfanView-style image browser with rating/renaming
Rating prefixes:
  5 → ____  (orange)   4 → ___  (purple)   3 → __  (blue)
  2 → _     (green)    1 → =    (white)     0 → zzz_trash_ (red)
  unrated → -  (auto-applied in single viewer, toggleable)

Requirements: pip install Pillow
"""

